{"id":1284,"date":"2023-03-07T19:15:20","date_gmt":"2023-03-07T13:15:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/the-benefits-of-hiring-a-professional-painter-for-your-home-2\/"},"modified":"2023-03-08T02:25:14","modified_gmt":"2023-03-07T20:25:14","slug":"the-dos-and-donts-of-painting-your-homes-exterior","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/the-dos-and-donts-of-painting-your-homes-exterior\/","title":{"rendered":"The dos and don&#8217;ts of painting your home&#8217;s exterior"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Choosing the right paint for your space can be a daunting task. With so many different colors, finishes, and brands to choose from, it can be overwhelming to know where to start. The right paint color can completely transform a room, creating a cohesive and inviting space that reflects your personal style and taste. On the other hand, the wrong paint color can be a source of frustration and disappointment.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Fortunately, choosing the right paint for your space doesn&#8217;t have to be a difficult or stressful process. In this blog post, we&#8217;ll provide some tips and considerations to help you choose the right paint for your space. From considering the room&#8217;s function and lighting to testing the paint and choosing high-quality products, we&#8217;ll cover everything you need to know to make an informed and confident decision. Whether you&#8217;re looking to refresh a single room or repaint your entire home, these tips will help you choose the perfect paint color for your space. So let&#8217;s get started!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/painting-the-walls-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"Painting the walls\" class=\"wp-image-135\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/painting-the-walls-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/painting-the-walls-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/painting-the-walls-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/painting-the-walls-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/painting-the-walls-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/painting-the-walls.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Consider the room&#8217;s function:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The first thing to consider when choosing paint is the room&#8217;s function. For example, a bedroom may benefit from a calming and relaxing color, while a home office may need a more energizing and stimulating color.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Take lighting into account:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The lighting in a room can greatly impact the color of the paint. Consider how much natural light the room receives, and whether the light is warm or cool toned. This can help determine whether a warm or cool toned paint color would work best.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Choose the right finish:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Different finishes, such as matte, satin, and gloss, can have a big impact on the overall look and feel of a room. Matte finishes provide a smooth and non-reflective look, while gloss finishes provide a shiny and reflective look. Consider the room&#8217;s use and traffic when choosing the right finish.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Test before committing:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s important to test the paint color before committing to a full room. Purchase a small sample and paint a small area on the wall to see how the color looks in different lighting and at different times of the day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-2 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/paint-roller-to-paint.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" data-id=\"57\" src=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/paint-roller-to-paint-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"Paint roller to paint\" class=\"wp-image-57\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/paint-roller-to-paint-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/paint-roller-to-paint-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/paint-roller-to-paint-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/paint-roller-to-paint-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/paint-roller-to-paint-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/paint-roller-to-paint.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/boyfriend-and-girlfriend-painting-wall-with-blue-paint.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"684\" data-id=\"81\" src=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/boyfriend-and-girlfriend-painting-wall-with-blue-paint-1024x684.jpg\" alt=\"boyfriend and girlfriend painting wall with blue paint\" class=\"wp-image-81\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/boyfriend-and-girlfriend-painting-wall-with-blue-paint-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/boyfriend-and-girlfriend-painting-wall-with-blue-paint-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/boyfriend-and-girlfriend-painting-wall-with-blue-paint-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/boyfriend-and-girlfriend-painting-wall-with-blue-paint-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/boyfriend-and-girlfriend-painting-wall-with-blue-paint-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/boyfriend-and-girlfriend-painting-wall-with-blue-paint.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/two-painters-painting-the-wall.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" data-id=\"176\" src=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/two-painters-painting-the-wall-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"Two painters painting the wall\" class=\"wp-image-176\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/two-painters-painting-the-wall-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/two-painters-painting-the-wall-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/two-painters-painting-the-wall-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/two-painters-painting-the-wall-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/two-painters-painting-the-wall-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/two-painters-painting-the-wall.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rear-view-of-couple-painting-wall-with-white-paint-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"684\" data-id=\"137\" src=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rear-view-of-couple-painting-wall-with-white-paint-1-1024x684.jpg\" alt=\"rear view of couple painting wall with white paint\" class=\"wp-image-137\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rear-view-of-couple-painting-wall-with-white-paint-1-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rear-view-of-couple-painting-wall-with-white-paint-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rear-view-of-couple-painting-wall-with-white-paint-1-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rear-view-of-couple-painting-wall-with-white-paint-1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rear-view-of-couple-painting-wall-with-white-paint-1-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rear-view-of-couple-painting-wall-with-white-paint-1.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Don&#8217;t be afraid to mix and match:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Experimenting with different colors and finishes can lead to unexpected and beautiful results. Don&#8217;t be afraid to mix and match different paint colors and finishes to create a unique and personalized space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Choose high-quality paint:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Investing in high-quality paint can make a big difference in the longevity and overall look of your painted space. High-quality paints often have better coverage, durability, and resistance to fading and wear.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In conclusion, choosing the right paint for your space requires careful consideration of the room&#8217;s function, lighting, finish, and color. Testing the paint before committing to a full room and not being afraid to mix and match can also lead to beautiful and unique results. Finally, investing in high-quality paint can ensure a long-lasting and beautiful finish.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Choosing the right paint for your space can be a daunting task. With so many different colors, finishes, and brands to choose from, it can be overwhelming to know where to start. The right paint color can completely transform a room, creating a cohesive and inviting space that reflects your personal style and taste. On [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":81,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1284","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-general"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1284","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1284"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1284\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1319,"href":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1284\/revisions\/1319"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/81"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1284"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1284"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.paintsplatter.oxaart.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1